mapper.select: SELECT Round(SUM( ( TO_DATE( ( SUBSTR( tbl.end_time, 1, 4 ) || '-' || SUBSTR( tbl.end_time, 5, 2 ) || '-' || SUBSTR( tbl.end_time, 7, 2 ) || ' ' || SUBSTR( tbl.end_time, 9, 2 ) || ':' || SUBSTR( tbl.end_time, 11, 2 ) || ':' || SUBSTR( tbl.end_time, 13, 2 ) ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS' ) - TO_DATE( ( SUBSTR( tbl.start_time, 1, 4 ) || '-' || SUBSTR( tbl.start_time, 5, 2 ) || '-' || SUBSTR( tbl.start_time, 7, 2 ) || ' ' || SUBSTR( tbl.start_time, 9, 2 ) || ':' || SUBSTR( tbl.start_time, 11, 2 ) || ':' || SUBSTR( tbl.start_time, 13, 2 ) ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS' ) )*24*3600 )) FROM ( SELECT tsc_id, ( CASE WHEN start_time < #{dateFromForDownTime} THEN #{dateFromForDownTime} ELSE start_time END ) start_time, ( CASE WHEN end_time = '9999999999999999' THEN #{dateToForDownTime} WHEN end_time > #{dateToForDownTime} THEN #{dateToForDownTime} ELSE end_time END ) end_time FROM down_time WHERE end_time <> '9999999999999999' AND start_time < #{dateToForDownTime} AND end_time > #{dateFromForDownTime} AND start_time < end_time AND tsc_id = #{tscId} ) tbl GROUP BY tbl.tsc_id
